        Bans this IP address
        Parameters:
        source - The UUID of the banner
        reason - The reason for the ban
        isTemp - True if the ban is temporary
        expiry - The Epoch milliseconds that the ban will expire at, use 0L if it is a permanent ban
        isShadow - True if the ban is a shadow ban
